text: Akademichesky (masculine), Akademicheskaya (feminine), or Akademicheskoye (neuter) may refer to: *Akademichesky District, a district of South-Western Administrative Okrug of Moscow, Russia *Akademicheskaya (Moscow Metro), a station of the Moscow Metro, Moscow, Russia *Akademicheskaya (Saint Petersburg Metro), a station of the Saint Petersburg Metro, Saint Petersburg, Russia *Akademicheskoye Municipal Okrug, a municipal okrug of Kalininsky District of Saint Petersburg, Russia
title: Akademichesky
